Explore Google Health Trends child abuse-related search term test runs

One sentence summary about objective of this doc to explore google health trends for child abuse-related search terms by examining data for 2019 (prior to study period).

Weekly searches at the national level for 2019:

Terms include variations of: what are signs of child abuse, [perpetrator] abuses me, how to tell if [male partner] is abusing child

Perpetrators included: mom, mother, stepmom, stepmother, moms boyfriend, mom boyfriend, moms girlfriend, mom girlfriend, moms friend, mom friend, dad, father, stepdad, stepfather, dads girlfriend, dad girlfriend, dads friend, dad friend, dads boyfriend, dad boyfriend, grandma, grandpa, brother, sister, uncle, aunt
